InformationText { Don't you feel at home in Drova?<br>Are you strong and wish to work?<br>You have come to the right place!<br>Here, you shall be paid for your hard work, and you shall have a place to sleep and a hot meal a day!<br><br>Become a Hewer and start prospecting silver!<br>You don't need to commit to anything — you can leave whenever you want, and you don't need to return.<br>Should you prove yourself as a Hewer, you might even be able to become a part of the Remnants' camp — as a fighter!<br><br>Come to the Pit, and report to Levin or Jola at the entrance to the Remnants' camp.<br><br>May the Red Tower protect you! }

